OL,7,FCharges weren't brought on her behalf,
OL,8,Fbut she is a former pupil of Foden's.
OL,9,FNo longer a child, she says he
OL,10,Fpromised to help when she was being
OL,11,Fbullied.
OL,13,F"When I started seeing him, I thought
OL,14,Fhe was quite nice, so that was a big
