OL,7,FShe describes meetings in his office:
OL,8,F"If I was upset, he'd start rubbing my
OL,9,Farm or my leg, and occasionally he'd
OL,10,Ftry to look up my skirt if I was sat
OL,11,Fin front of him.
OL,13,F"And that progressed to him hugging me
OL,14,Fwhen I was upset. And he would just
