OL,7,FHe urged his victims to keep quiet,
OL,8,Ftelling one she must "take it to the
OL,9,Fgrave".
OL,11,FThe highly critical report published
OL,12,Fon Tuesday looks at the time period
OL,13,Fbetween January 2017 and 30 September
OL,14,F2023, and highlights numerous
OL,15,Finstances when individuals and
OL,16,Fagencies reported concerns about
OL,17,FFoden's inappropriate contact with
OL,18,Fteenage girls.
OL,20,FIt includes times he was seen alone
OL,21,Fwith them and giving them lifts.
